## 3. Local Development Deployment

### 3.1 Clone Project

```bash
git clone <repository-url>
cd customer-communication-dashboard
```

### 3.2 Copy Environment File

```bash
cp backend/.env.example backend/.env
cp frontend/.env.example frontend/.env
```

### 3.3 Run Services

```bash
docker compose up -d --build
```

### 3.4 Check Containers

```bash
docker compose ps
```

Expected running services:

```text
postgres
redis
minio
backend
frontend
worker
```

### 3.5 Health Check

```bash
curl http://localhost:8080/health
```

Expected response:

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Service is healthy",
  "data": {
    "app": "ok",
    "postgres": "ok",
    "redis": "ok",
    "minio": "ok"
  }
}
```

### 3.6 Access Frontend

```text
http://localhost:5173
```

### 3.7 Access MinIO Console

```text
http://localhost:9001
```

Default development credential:

```text
Username: minioadmin
Password: minioadmin123
```

