## 4. Docker Compose Production Deployment

### 4.1 Prepare VPS

```bash
sudo apt update
sudo apt install -y docker.io docker-compose-plugin nginx certbot python3-certbot-nginx
sudo systemctl enable docker
sudo systemctl start docker
```

### 4.2 Upload Project to VPS

```bash
git clone <repository-url>
cd customer-communication-dashboard
```

### 4.3 Configure Environment

Create production env:

```bash
cp backend/.env.example backend/.env
cp frontend/.env.example frontend/.env
```

Edit backend env:

```env
APP_ENV=production
APP_PORT=8080

DB_HOST=postgres
DB_PORT=5432
DB_USER=postgres
DB_PASSWORD=change-secure-password
DB_NAME=cs_dashboard

JWT_SECRET=change-very-secure-jwt-secret

REDIS_HOST=redis
REDIS_PORT=6379
REDIS_PASSWORD=

MINIO_ENDPOINT=minio:9000
MINIO_ACCESS_KEY=change-minio-user
MINIO_SECRET_KEY=change-minio-password
MINIO_BUCKET=chat-media
MINIO_USE_SSL=false

TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=
TELEGRAM_WEBHOOK_SECRET=

WHATSAPP_PROVIDER=cloud_api
WHATSAPP_ACCESS_TOKEN=
WHATSAPP_PHONE_NUMBER_ID=
WHATSAPP_VERIFY_TOKEN=
```

Frontend env:

```env
VITE_API_URL=https://api.yourdomain.com
```

### 4.4 Run Production

```bash
docker compose up -d --build
```

### 4.5 Check Logs

```bash
docker compose logs -f backend
docker compose logs -f worker
docker compose logs -f frontend
```

