## 12. Rollback Strategy

For Docker Compose:

```bash
git checkout <previous-commit>
docker compose up -d --build
```

For Kubernetes:

```bash
kubectl rollout undo deployment/backend -n cs-dashboard
kubectl rollout undo deployment/frontend -n cs-dashboard
kubectl rollout undo deployment/worker -n cs-dashboard
```

---

## 13. Backup Strategy

### PostgreSQL Backup

```bash
docker exec -t postgres pg_dump -U postgres cs_dashboard > backup.sql
```

### PostgreSQL Restore

```bash
cat backup.sql | docker exec -i postgres psql -U postgres -d cs_dashboard
```

### MinIO Backup

Backup MinIO data volume regularly.

Recommended:

```text
Daily backup for database
Weekly backup for MinIO files
Retention: 7 daily, 4 weekly, 3 monthly
```

---

## 14. Production Recommendation

For MVP:

```text
VPS + Docker Compose
```

For scalable production:

```text
Kubernetes + managed PostgreSQL + managed Redis + external object storage
```

Do not start with Kubernetes unless the MVP core features are stable.
